        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Mental Health Research Accelerator Act of 2022</strong></p> <p>This bill allows a tax credit through 2031 for 25% of expenses for translational research regarding neurodegenerative diseases and psychiatric conditions. The credit amount is subject to limitations, including an aggregate national limitation of $1 billion in 2022, $2 billion in 2023-2027, and $1 billion in 2028.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
